---
title: Pan-Seared Chicken with Yukon Potatoes, Green Beans, and Creamy Dill Sauce
description: We’ve cracked the code to creating crowd-pleasing dinners: sauce! Everyone loves a creamy sauce draped over juicy chicken. This sauce is spiked with a touch of Dijon mustard and fresh dill for brightness.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/uk-pan-fried-chicken-f-1eaaef61.jpg
